CatDescriptText: Trumpeter Boonie Hazen played with Fletcher Henderson.
TitMainTitle: Thay Whitely on saxophone, Gordon "Slick" Jackson on piano, Bob Lowery on drums, and Marion "Boonie" Hazel on trumpet, performing in old Musician's Club with "TW" on music stand, and sign on wall reading "Talent Nite and Jam Session every Friday from 10 to ?"
